podsleuth: podsleuth (iPod (TM) Mono Discovery and Metadata Tool)
podsleuth:
podsleuth: PodSleuth is a tool to discover detailed model information about 
podsleuth: an Apple iPod (TM). Its primary role is a callout by HAL to scan 
podsleuth: the device for required information. When the model information 
podsleuth: is discovered, it is merged into HAL as properties for other 
podsleuth: applications to use.  With PodSleuth installed, applications 
podsleuth: can expect to have rich iPod metadata merged into the device 
podsleuth: tree on the iPod data volume node.
podsleuth:
